attributeExpressionDescription: Narrow down features of interest based on attribute values in a field.
expressionDescription: Filter down records of interest based on field values.
expressionGroupDescription: Group criteria to control order and relationships within the query.
spatialExpressionDescription: Narrow down features of interest based on spatial relationships with features in another layer.
spatialExpressionTwoLayers: Spatial expressions require at least two distinct layers.
